    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "sec9_c1_t",
      "x": 92,
      "y": 2120,
      "width": 486,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "Speculative Decoding\n— speculative/ + models/llama_eagle3.py\n• EAGLE3 / MTP Draft model accelerates AR generation\n• Draft many tokens, target verifies once\n• Toggled via Scheduler.spec_algorithm\n• Near N× throughput when accept rate is high",
      "originalText": "Speculative Decoding\n— speculative/ + models/llama_eagle3.py\n• EAGLE3 / MTP Draft model accelerates AR generation\n• Draft many tokens, target verifies once\n• Toggled via Scheduler.spec_algorithm\n• Near N× throughput when accept rate is high",
