      "id": "sec9_c2_t",
      "x": 622,
      "y": 2120,
      "width": 486,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "LoRA Adapter\n— lora/ · LoRAManager\n• Dynamically load multiple Adapters, switch per request\n• Shared base weights + independent A/B low-rank\n• Cache isolation prevents cross-contamination\n• ScheduleBatch groups by lora_path",
      "originalText": "LoRA Adapter\n— lora/ · LoRAManager\n• Dynamically load multiple Adapters, switch per request\n• Shared base weights + independent A/B low-rank\n• Cache isolation prevents cross-contamination\n• ScheduleBatch groups by lora_path",
