      "type": "text",
      "id": "sec9_c3_t",
      "x": 1152,
      "y": 2120,
      "width": 486,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "Quantization\n— configs/ · utils/quantization\n• INT8 / FP8 / INT4 weight quantization\n• Static (offline) and dynamic (per-shard) dual paths\n• Linear is converted to quantized_matmul backend\n• mimo_v2_pro integrated with Fused QKV + FP8",
      "originalText": "Quantization\n— configs/ · utils/quantization\n• INT8 / FP8 / INT4 weight quantization\n• Static (offline) and dynamic (per-shard) dual paths\n• Linear is converted to quantized_matmul backend\n• mimo_v2_pro integrated with Fused QKV + FP8",
