      "y": 2120,
      "width": 486,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "MoE / EPMoE (with EPLB)\n— layers/moe · FusedMoE / EPMoE\n• Top-K gating + expert routing\n• EP (Expert Parallel) cross-device dispatch\n• EPLB sub-feature: dynamic load rebalancing\n• Qwen MoE / DeepSeek V3 / Bailing",
      "originalText": "MoE / EPMoE (with EPLB)\n— layers/moe · FusedMoE / EPMoE\n• Top-K gating + expert routing\n• EP (Expert Parallel) cross-device dispatch\n• EPLB sub-feature: dynamic load rebalancing\n• Qwen MoE / DeepSeek V3 / Bailing",
