    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t3_t",
      "x": 122,
      "y": 1724,
      "width": 456,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "KV / State Buffer   (memory_pool.py · recurrent_state_pool.py)\n• MHATokenToKVPool       — default MHA / GQA actual K/V pool\n• MLATokenToKVPool       — DeepSeek MLA latent KV\n• SWAKVPool              — Sliding Window local window KV\n• RecurrentStatePool     — KDA / Mamba / GDN linear recurrent",
      "originalText": "KV / State Buffer   (memory_pool.py · recurrent_state_pool.py)\n• MHATokenToKVPool       — default MHA / GQA actual K/V pool\n• MLATokenToKVPool       — DeepSeek MLA latent KV\n• SWAKVPool              — Sliding Window local window KV\n• RecurrentStatePool     — KDA / Mamba / GDN linear recurrent",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a8a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
